      <p>The Administration Area is held simple without in-depth menus that would need explanation. As an administrator you can manage and add channels. 
Being an owner of a channel allows you to subscribe and unsubscribe users. You can also define whether the channel is <strong>public</strong> so that users can subscribe without your verification, <strong>global</strong>, meaning the channel is visible from external nodes and clients, or <strong>none</strong> of the above.
