      <h2>Groups and Individuals</h2>
      <p>Users can be assigned to group to ease the administration. The groups can be given rights and access to specific channels and file folders. A member of a group automatically has the same rights of the group.</p>
      <p>Individual users can be added to the channels by user name, ID or e-mail address. Individuals can, but do not need to, belong to one or more groups. If needed, rights can be altered individually. Each channel has their individual ID that can be given to a third party, for example to a customer you need to work together with.</p>
